      • registerErrorTypes

        public void registerErrorTypes(java.util.List<ErrorType> errors)
        Registers a list of ErrorTypes to be used by the configured stub for resolving VMODL2 errors received as result of a method invocation.

        The types for all standard VMODL2 errors are registered and resolvable by default. This method is useful for registration of additional types for custom errors.

        Parameters:
        errors - types to register; can not be null; can not contain null elements
